Package: openmux
Architecture: all
Depends: adduser, ${python3:Depends}, ${misc:Depends},
 python3-aiohttp, python3-jinja2, python3-websockets,
 python3-cryptography, python3-serial, python3-serial-asyncio,
 python3-yaml, python3-six
Recommends: python3-pam
Description: Serial port multiplexing server and client
 OpenMux is a serial/console multiplexer and remote access service. It
 provides a server with adapters for loopback, serial, command, and
 federation (muxcon), plus a web console and local control CLI.
 .
 This package installs the Python modules into dist-packages and exposes
 console scripts similar to pip installation:
  - openmux-server
  - openmux-client
  - openmuxctl%
